更具艺术思维，抽象和感性认知的大脑。<br>逻辑和控制，涉及到更多细节，更多的利我们的左脑，也就是更熟悉概念和理性的半边。<br>其实有整个大脑自然好于只有一边，但是我们的教育体系一直在锻炼我们的左脑，而弱化右脑，大家从小到大都沉浸在灌输概念，讲究理性的推理，从而使得右脑荒废，这也是为什么很多成年人画画甚至不如幼儿园小孩的原因。因为小时候我们的世界还是两边大脑一起发展的。<br>现在深度学习的推理框架中，MXNet就是一个很好的结合了申明式和指令式编程的算法框架，这也让它在深度学习领悟大受欢迎","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1052859,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/10/bb/f1061601.jpg","nickname":"Demon.Lee","note":"","ucode":"7F0E5493A8E345","race_medal":1,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":297109,"discussion_content":"为啥我的理解是：声明式解决的是逻辑和控制的问题，指令式解决的是算法和数据的问题。把逻辑和控制分开，应该是右脑干的事吧，不陷入细节中去。欢迎讨论。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1596780088,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":1,"child_discussions":[{"author":{"id":1177602,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/f8/02/a02d127d.jpg","nickname":"Treasure","note":"","ucode":"4211ECEB347C3D","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":1052859,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/10/bb/f1061601.jpg","nickname":"Demon.Lee","note":"","ucode":"7F0E5493A8E345","race_medal":1,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":310915,"discussion_content":"我觉得这个分类就不对，不是算法 = 控制 +逻辑 吗，本来就不是很好理解，现在又 一边 数据+算法，一边 逻辑 +控制…\n就是一边控制(how to do) 一边 逻辑 (do waht)  这样分我觉得好一些。 ","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1602128073,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":297109,"ip_address":""},"score":310915,"extra":""}]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":252107,"user_name":"Treasure","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1177602,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4211ECEB347C3D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/f8/02/a02d127d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1602127841,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"5897095137","product_id":100002201,"comment_content":"「我们再归纳一下，基本上来说，就是两大分支，一边是在解决数据和算法，一边是在解决逻辑和控制。」<br><br>这个说错了吧。本来 逻辑 和控制就不是号很好理解，你这里的归纳怎么又成了 一边 数据和算法，一边逻辑和控制了？<br><br>逻辑 + 控制不是 等于算法么…<br><br>我认为是命令式 多是控制流转，解决的是控制，像迭代就是最典型的命令式思维。<br><br>而 声明式 是do what，而不是how to do 而且，其实分割没有那么明显，就像过程式的函数名 不就是 do what 么，里面的实现是 how to do<br>","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2309641,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/DYAIOgq83er4IPqj4H3jQHq4C1lgKh6ZroK3CVmGLiadic7S1rxbuy09JM9x8Aib6VkozPkO4lrUTHAhicX1z9Cg2w/132","nickname":"seedjyh","note":"","ucode":"D590E526A9A1D7","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":406085,"discussion_content":"应该说是两种解耦方式，一边是把数据和算法解耦，另一边是把逻辑和控制解耦。这样就比较容易理解了。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1634698605,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":212169,"user_name":"未来小娃","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1047329,"ip_address":"","ucode":"477D166EBB6B70","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/fb/21/d017438c.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1588070003,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5883037299","product_id":100002201,"comment_content":"高阶程序员拼的事认知，善于讲复杂得问题模型化抽象化，这点需要在日常工作的积极思考和探索。祝进步","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":210657,"user_name":"刘清斌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1123103,"ip_address":"","ucode":"775B053AF87B53","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/23/1f/6452b2e8.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1587803928,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score